|image = |caption = |competition = [[Tonga Major League|Tongatapu Inter Club Championship]]|season = 1988|winners = [[Ngele'ia FC]]|premiers = |promoted = |relegated = |matches = |total goals = |average goals = |league topscorer = |biggest home win = |biggest away win = |highest scoring = |attendance = |average attendance = |prevseason = [[1987 Tongatapu Inter Club Championship|1987]]|nextseason = [[1989 Tongatapu Inter Club Championship|1989]]}}The 1988 season of the [[Tonga Major League|Tongatapu Inter Club Championship]] was the 15th season of top flight [[association football]] competition in [[Tonga]]. [[Ngeleʻia FC]] won the championship for the seventh time, their final title in a then-record of 7 consecutive championships.<ref name="RSSSF22">{{Cite web|title = Tonga 1988|url = http://www.rsssf.com/tablest/tonga88.html|website = www.rsssf.com|access-date = 2016-02-21}}</ref>

