'''Cebeci Sport Hall''' ({{lang-tr|Cebeci Spor Salonu}}) is an indoor multi-purpose sport venue that is located in the [[Sultangazi]], [[Istanbul]], [[Turkey]]. The hall, with a capacity for 1,250 spectators, was built in 2012.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.istanbulsporenvanteri.com/tr/tesisler/tesisler-2/ibb-cebeci-spor-kompleksi-546.html |publisher=istanbulsporenvanteri.com |title= İBB CEBECİ SPOR KOMPLEKSİ  |language=Turkish |accessdate=2015-01-03 }}</ref> It is home to [[İstanbul Büyükşehir Belediyespor (basketball)|İstanbul BB]], which plays currently in the [[Turkish Basketball League]].


