'''Diyala football club''' ({{lang-ar|'''نادي ديالى'''}}), is an [[Iraq]]i football club based in [[Diyala Governorate|Diyala]]. The team was demoted from the first division after the [[Iraqi Premier League 2005-06|2005–06]] season and finally they got promoted and will compete in [[Iraqi Premier League 2008–09|2008–09]].
After one year spell in the top division they got relegated to the Iraq second division

