{{Infobox football biography |name = Haruna Mawa |image = |image_size = |caption = |fullname = |birth_date = |birth_place = Uganda |death_date = |death_place = |currentclub = |manageryears1 = ?–2016 |managerclubs1 = SC Victoria University |manageryears2 = 2016–2017 |managerclubs2 = Somalia }}
'''Haruna Mawa''' is a [[Uganda]]n football coach and former footballer.
As a player, he played for Rayon Sports FC in Rwanda.<ref>http://www.rsssf.com/tablesc/cecafa05.html</ref>
In November 2016, he was appointed as coach of the [[Somalia national football team]].<ref>http://www.hiiraan.com/news4/2016/Nov/128545/haruna_appointed_somalia_coach.aspx</ref>
