'''KF Drenica''' ({{lang-sq|Klubi Futbollistik Drenica}}), commonly known as '''Drenica''' is a professional [[Football team|football club]] based in [[Skenderaj]], [[Kosovo]]. The club play in the [[Football Superleague of Kosovo]], which is the top tier of football in the country.

