'''Stade Al-Merghani Kassala''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Kassala]], in northeastern [[Sudan]].  It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home stadium of [[Al-Merrikh]].  <br />
The Stadium has a capacity of 11,000 people.

