{{Infobox national volleyball team |name=Tajikistan |gender=women |image=Flag of Tajikistan.svg |federation=[[Volleyball Federation of Tajikistan]] |website= |confederation=AVC |manager= |coach= |Olympic apps=0 |World Champs apps=0 }}
The '''Tajikistan women's national volleyball team''' is the national women's volleyball team of [[Tajikistan]].
Most notable Tajikstan-born female volleyballer is [[Angelina Grün]] who formerly represented [[Germany women%27s national volleyball team|Germany]].
